---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact">
  <section class="prose max-w-none text-sm text-gray-300">
    <h1>Contact WSM Live Terminal</h1>
    <p>Please reach out to our team using the contact information below. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48 business hours.</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mt-6 mb-3">Contact Email Addresses</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
      <li><strong>General Admin Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@wsmlive.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">admin@wsmlive.com</a></li>
      <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@wsmlive.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">support@wsmlive.com</a></li>
      <li><strong>General Inquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@wsmlive.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@wsmlive.com</a></li>
      <li><strong>Privacy & Legal:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@wsmlive.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">contact@wsmlive.com</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mt-6 mb-3">More Information</h2>
    <p>For detailed information about our services, privacy practices, and terms, please visit our <a href="/legal" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Legal & Support page</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>